thread.title: Rhonda Holt

author: Rhonda Holt
title: Rhonda Holt
text: I was a bit nervous about using this site for the first time as I had not heard of it. Being an older house bound lady it is great to know this site exists. Web site is easy to use and all trades have been thoroughly police . Funds deposited are secure until YOU release them on completion of works requested. All my reservations were for naught s this site and works are top quality and trust worthy.
